step_data.thought:
I've successfully updated the 'Notify for Quantity Below' field to '10' in the Advanced Inventory dialog and clicked 'Done' to confirm those changes. However, these changes are not yet saved to the product itself. I need to save the entire product to ensure the inventory threshold changes are permanently applied.

Looking at the page, I can see a 'Save' button (bid 869) in the main action bar at the top of the page. This button will save all changes made to the product, including the inventory threshold update I just made.

Let me click the 'Save' button to finalize the changes to the Fitness Tracker Pro product.
